.SH "SHExpandGLQ"
.IX Header "SHExpandGLQ"
.IP "SHExpandGLQ \-" 14
.IX Item "SHExpandGLQ -"
Expand a 2D grid sampled on the Gauss-Legendre quadrature nodes into spherical harmonics.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.IP "\s-1SUBROUTINE\s0 SHExpandGLQ (" 25
.IX Item "SUBROUTINE SHExpandGLQ ("
\&\s-1CILM, LMAX, GRIDGLQ, W, PLX, ZERO, NORM, CSPHASE, LMAX_CALC \s0)
.RS 4
.IP "REAL*8" 19
.IX Item "REAL*8"
\&\s-1CILM\s0(2, \s-1LMAX+1, LMAX+1\s0) \fIor\fR \s-1CILM\s0(2,\ \s-1LMAX_CALC+1,\s0\ \s-1LMAX_CALC+1\s0), \s-1GRIDGLQ\s0(\s-1LMAX+1,\s0\ 2*LMAX+1), W(\s-1LMAX+1\s0)
